CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 7, 2011

[Cite as 03/07/2011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-976.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2010-1570. State ex rel. Zeigler v. Allbritain.

In Quo Warranto. Upon consideration of relator’s request for oral argument, it is ordered by the court that the motion is granted. Oral argument is scheduled for Wednesday, March 23, 2011.
